BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:bGYLru2ZQICx7c4_lgx5C
SUMMARY:2026 Seattle Sister Cities Soup Sampling
DTSTAMP:20260308T004817Z
DTSTART:20260308T140000Z
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate International Women’s Day at the 2nd annual Seattle S
	ister Cities’ Soup Sampling\\\, sponsored by the Seattle Sister Cities Ass
	ociation in partnership with the National Nordic Museum. The Soup Sampling
	 is a community event where volunteer cooks from 11 Seattle Sister Cities 
	share popular international soups representing four continents. Guests nee
	d to bring only a smile and an interest in tasting new recipes and learnin
	g about diverse cultures. Please register for the event before March 1st\;
	 walk-in admission will not be available. \\nThis is a cultural event that
	 includes five soup tastings per entry. Donations of $10 per person are en
	couraged and benefit the nonprofit Seattle Sister Cities Association to su
	pport cultural\\\, educational\\\, and humanitarian programs. (When reserv
	ing tickets\\\, your donation will result in 1 admission ticket. Use the q
	uantity selector to reserve tickets for additional attendees). From Seattl
	e’s 20 sister cities\\\, the following will be represented at this event: 
	Reykjavik\\\, Iceland\; Bergen\\\, Norway\; Pecs\\\, Hungary\; Be’er Sheva
	\\\, Israel\; Christchurch\\\, New Zealand\; Mombasa\\\, Kenya\; Sihanoukv
	ille\\\, Cambodia\; Perugia\\\, Italy\; Surabaya\\\, Indonesia\; Hai Phong
	\\\, Vietnam\; and Kobe\\\, Japan. \\nAttendees are also encouraged to vis
	it New Nordic: Cuisine\\\, Aesthetics and Place as well as other exhibits 
	at the National Nordic Museum and will get 50% off admission on the day of
	 this event\n\nhttps://myballard.com/event/2026-seattle-sister-cities-soup
	-sampling/\n\nFrom My Ballard
URL:https://myballard.com/event/2026-seattle-sister-cities-soup-sampling/
LOCATION:National Nordic Museum\\\, 2655 NW Market Street\\\, Seattle\\\, W
	A\\\, 98107\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:myballard
CATEGORIES:My Ballard
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
