DESCRIPTION:Have you ever wanted to color with thread? In this class we’ll 
	do just that! With hands-on guidance from fiber artist and author\\\, Meli
	ssa Galbraith\\\, you’ll enjoy a 3-hour workshop learning the basics of th
	read painting\\\, stitching on tulle fabric\\\, and stumpwork embroidery t
	o create a pair of botanical earrings. No matter if you’re an experienced 
	embroiderer or new to stitching\\\, in this class we’ll practice stitches 
	needed to thread paint and create 3D ginkgo earrings. All materials are in
	cluded for class to create wearable 3D embroidery.\n\nhttps://myballard.co
