BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:I2s61HHEg6zrsF_rldJEt
SUMMARY:On Point Live with Meghna Chakrabarti
DTSTAMP:20260308T004817Z
DTSTART:20260331T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join KUOW for a special live taping of On Point with Meghna Cha
	krabarti Tuesday\\\, March 31 at Town Hall Seattle. \\nSeattle’s mayor\\\,
	 socialist Katie Wilson\\\, won one of the tightest elections in the city’
	s history last year. Now\\\, three months into the job\\\, how is her prog
	ressive agenda taking shape — and what might national Democrats learn from
	 her early leadership? \\nJoin On Point host Meghna Chakrabarti on Tuesday
